contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox French commune |name = Quissac |region = [[Midi-Pyrénées]] |department = [[Lot (département)|Lot]] |arrondissement = [[Arrondissement of Figeac]] |canton = [[Canton of Livernon]] |INSEE = 46233 |postal code = 46320 |mayor = '''Alain Fogarizzu''' |term = 2001–2008 |intercommunality = [[Communauté de communes de la Vallée et du Causse]] |longitude = 1.7311 |latitude = 44.6458 |elevation m = 117 |elevation min m = 269 |elevation max m = 455 |area km2 = 25.17 |population = 106 |population date = 1 999 }} '''Quissac''' is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Lot (department)|Lot]] [[Departments of France|department]] in south-western France. ==See also== *[[Communes of the Lot department]] {{Lot communes}} [[Category:Communes of Lot (department)]] {{Lot-geo-stub}}
